description:
* Windows 7 SP1 Ultimate X64 incl Office 2010 en-US May 2017


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* File: W7X64.ULT.OFF14.ENU.MAY.2017.iso
* Size: 4,00GB
* Format: Bootable ISO

* CRC32: 8394c348
* MD5: 053d7600c6d87745978b609166211509
* SHA-1: 06725915dcde918960c12ba68a069ef98213c6d8

[ SOURCE ]

* X17-59465

[ LANGUAGE ]

* ENGLISH US 

[ CONTENTS ]

* Integrated / Pre-installed:

* .NET Framework 4.7
* Internet Explorer 11
* Important & Security Updates - 2017-05-09
* Office 2010 Pro Plus VL - Updated 2017-04-26  

* Setupcomplete / Post-install:

* DirectX End-User Runtimes (June 2010)
* Windows Defender Updates

[ FEATURES ]

* UEFI-ready 
* (Use attached Rufus USB-tool to make UEFI-bootable)
* install.wim compressed to recovery format (install.esd)
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10.0 (Microsoft DaRT)

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

* Windows 7 Ultimate incl Office 2010

* Activators: Daz Loader v2.2.2.0 & KMSpico
( Both Activators Potential False Positive Virus Alarm )

[ Activation instructions ]

* A WPI-window will pop up in the last phase of the installation.  
* For Windows activation, select "Daz Loader". 
* For Office activation, select "KMSpico".
* To execute your choises, click on "Begin Install".
* To skip activation, just click on "Exit".  

[ SCREENSHOTS ]

[url]https://extraimage.net/image/NitH[/url]

[ INSTALLATION & INFORMATION ]

* Create bootable USB (highly recommended) with Rufus,
* (attached) or burn to DVD at slow speed.

[ CREDITS ]

* ashish.k, milrob & stevie-boy for continued
* support & help with user questions.

* Hope you will enjoy this release!

* Regards,
* Generation2 @ KAT, TPB & 1337X
